$ CSS: orphans, widows

The → development/web/CSS/properties[CSS properties] `orphans` and `widows` specify the minum number of lines in a block container that must be shown at the bottom/top of a page, region or column.

sa:

 The → development/web/CSS/properties[CSS properties] → development/web/CSS/properties/page-break[`page-break-before`, `page-break-after` and `page-break-inside`]

  
